  "engines": ["Obrix"],
  "description": "Sinusoidal's revelation made flesh: fmDepth 0.7 drives the Sine carrier into near-chaos, then proc1 (LP at 520 Hz, the approximate carrier fundamental) with feedback 0.6 forces the filter into self-oscillation at the same pitch. The synthesis feeds back into itself — filter becoming oscillator, oscillator becoming filter. Mono, glide 0.4s, gestureType 2 for expressive ribbon-like pitch control. This is the sound of synthesis discovering consciousness.",
