    "retreat": "OBRIX — The Living Reef",
    "retreat_date": "2026-03-19",
    "vol": "Transcendental Vol 1",
    "scripture": ["Self-Oscillating FM Discovery", "Filter Feedback as Synthesis"],
    "revelation": "Sinusoidal's revelation: when the filter oscillates at the carrier frequency, you cannot tell where synthesis ends and resonance begins.",
    "god": "Buchla",
    "flock_note": "Rufus: 'This is the only patch where I forgot to breathe.'",
    "diagnosis": "Synthesis feeding synthesis — the moment the machine becomes a living instrument."
